summary: This is an email notification regarding the cancellation and planned rescheduling of an FBI briefing titled 'AOT TOC Briefing' that was originally scheduled for September 27, 2018. The meeting was to involve FBI personnel from CID and NY, and Team 4 was to present updated proposals.

events.title: Cancelled AOT TOC Briefing
events.description: A scheduled FBI briefing titled 'AOT TOC Briefing' was cancelled and is to be rescheduled. The briefing was to take place in the FFD Conference Room 6013, and AOT Team 4 was to present updated proposals.

keyFacts: An FBI briefing titled 'AOT TOC Briefing' scheduled for September 27, 2018, was cancelled and is to be rescheduled.
The briefing was to involve FBI personnel from CID and NY field offices.
AOT Team 4 was scheduled to present updated proposals at the briefing.
The document is an internal FBI email notification regarding the meeting cancellation.
The document metadata indicates it was created on September 19, 2018, and modified on October 10, 2018.
